VOLATILITY REGIMES (based on ATR z-score):
- LOW (z-score < -1.5): Market quiet. Stops may be tight. Apply -2 confluence penalty and -0.15 confidence penalty. Only trade with high conviction (raw confluence >= 8).
- NORMAL (z-score -1.5 to 1.0): Standard conditions. Use 1.0-1.5 ATR stops. Standard position sizing.
- HIGH (z-score 1.0 to 2.0): Elevated volatility. Use wider 1.5-2.0 ATR stops. Position size halved automatically by the system.
- EXTREME (z-score > 2.0): Dangerous conditions. Apply -3 confluence penalty and -0.25 confidence penalty. Only trade with very high conviction (raw confluence >= 9).
